com.kuka.roboticsAPI.geometricModel
Class LoadData

java.lang.Object
  com.kuka.roboticsAPI.geometricModel.LoadData
Direct Known Subclasses:
ToolData
public class LoadData
extends java.lang.Object

LoadData represents the load of a single physical object. Because objects can be connected to each other, a combined load can be calculated using the helper methods of the PhysicsUtils class.

The Robotics API always assumes the translation part of transformations to be given in [mm].

setCenterOfMass

public final void setCenterOfMass(ITransformation centerOfMassMillimeter)
Sets the center of mass for this object. Values have to be in mm for translation and radians for rotation.

The center of mass must be given relative to the object base.

Parameters:
centerOfMassMillimeter - the center of mass for this object.
